BanksRUs

Class CheckingAccount

  • java.lang.Object
    • BanksRUs.Account
      • BanksRUs.CheckingAccount

  • public class CheckingAccount
extends Account
    This class extends from the Account class, has all the functions and variables from it. This class has some extra variables which are only used in it. We can deposit to a checking account and withdraw if and only if if we don't go over the over draw limit, that the account has. We have also limit of free transactions which is given when we make an object of this account.
    Version:
    1.0, 1 sept 2016
    Author:
